WEBVTT

00:08.000 --> 00:16.000
Build, analyze, and automate trading strategies.

00:16.000 --> 00:25.000
A backtesting engine built so the usual backtest lies are structurally impossible.

00:25.000 --> 00:33.000
The same engine runs in the open — one reference strategy, net of costs, per run.

00:33.000 --> 00:42.000
Look-ahead-free by construction: decisions read only closed bars; orders fill next-bar open.

00:42.000 --> 00:48.000
Honest backtesting · an AI strategy copilot · live charting.

00:48.000 --> 00:55.000
A visual strategy builder, paper trading on the same engine, and risk-first gating.

00:55.000 --> 01:04.000
Costs on by default. Decimal money. No cherry-picked numbers — run your own backtest.
